name: 𝚃𝚄𝙻𝙿𝙰
description: How will spirituality deal with the integration of technology? How the beings of the spiritual realm will deal with the hardware that will compose the human body? Can ghosts, demons, and angels learn how to hack? In 𝚃𝚄𝙻𝙿𝙰, we foresee how a malignal influence from the astral realm can afflict the body and soul of it's victim, just like a malware corrupting a system.
